      "id": "prod-env-staging",
      "text": "Everyone has a testing environment. Some people are lucky enough to have a totally separate environment to run production in.",
      "author": "Unknown",
      "author_slug": "unknown",
      "source": "DevOps folklore",
      "categories": [
        "funny",
        "suffering"
      ],
      "tags": [
        "testing",
